
<div metal:use-macro="layout">
<div metal:fill-slot="content">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">About <strong>Arranca PR</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img width="400px" " src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/img/waterfall.jpg')}" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p>Arranca Pr is a non profit that started due to the concern of people in "diaspora" about the resources available for training and the capital available to acquire machinery in the island.</p>
                    <p>Our intention is to bring back "technical creation skills" via web-casting and by creating product prototype centers in the island(makerspaces).</p>
                    <p>Founded in 2013.</p>
                    <p>We are a non profit(501c3) in the island of Puerto Rico.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Our <strong>Volunteers</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/img/widalis.jpg')}" alt="">
                    <h3>Widalys Ramos
                        <small>Director</small>
                    </h3>
                    <p> <a href="mailto:widalys@arrancapr.org"></a> widalys@arrancapr.org </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/img/alfredo.jpg')}" alt="">
                    <h3>Alfredo Alvarez
                        <small>President</small>
                    </h3>
                    <p> <a href="mailto:alfredo@arrancapr.org"></a> alfredo@arrancapr.org </p>
                </div>

                 <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/img/edward.png')}" alt="">
                    <h3>Edward Betancourt
                        <small>Vice-President</small>
                    </h3>
                    <p> <a href="mailto:edward@arrancapr.org"></a> edward@arrancapr.org </p>
                </div>

                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

     <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Contact <strong>Arranca PR</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                 <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
                    <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
                    <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="S6K9BHKAJCY88">
                    <input type="image" src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
                    <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
                    </form>
                <p>For mail donations please send a check addressed to the following address:</p>
                <p><strong>Arranca P.R., Corp. <br>P.O. Box 70  .<br>Isabela P.R. 00662</strong>
                    </p>
                    <p>or via bank transfer contact us for details. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <p>Phone: <strong>(787)-528-0669 </strong>
                    </p>
                    <p>Email: <strong>arrancaprcorp@gmail.com</strong>
                    </p>

                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <i>ArrancaPR is a registered 501c3 organization.
                </div>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Contact <strong>form</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                    <p> Have a question or a proposition you want us to hear about? Please fill out the form below and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
                    <form role="form" method="POST" action="/about">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="form-group col-lg-4">
                                <label>Name</label>
                                <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-lg-4">
                                <label>Email Address</label>
                                <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-lg-4">
                                <label>Phone Number</label>
                                <input type="tel" name="tel" class="form-control">
                            </div>
                            <div class="clearfix"></div>
                            <div class="form-group col-lg-12">
                                <label>Message</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" name="body" rows="6"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-lg-12">
                                <input type="hidden" name="save" value="contact">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <!-- /.container -->

     <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/js/jquery-1.10.2.js')}"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="${request.static_url('arrancapr:static/js/bootstrap.js')}"></script>

</div>
